<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/stringstring/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1057103-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/stringstring/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">该石头不太冷</span>
